        <footnote id="F8">Shares subject to the option are fully vested. Pursuant to the Merger Agreement, the option was cancelled and converted into the right to receive a cash payment of $233,091.00, which represents the difference between $55.75 and the exercise price of the option per share multiplied by the number of shares subject to the option.</footnote>
